A1: s entry into the Customs Union
RelatedSentence: Kyrgyz Economic Minister , Temir Sariyev , while on a visit to Astana discussed Kyrgyzstan ' s entry into the Customs Union with Kazakhstan 's Deputy Prime Minister , Bakytzhan Sagintayev , the Kazakh prime minister 's official website announced on May 16 .
The two sides discussed the roadmap approved by the Kyrgyz government earlier this week for the country's entry into the CU , which consists presently of Belarus , Kazakhstan and Russia .
